STATE of North Carolina
v.
Vernon Ray TABOR. No. 248P04-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 6, 2007. Bruce T. Cunningham, Southern Pines, for Vernon Ray Tabor. Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General, Annette Sellars, Assistant District Attorney, Sam Currin, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 6th day of November 2007 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Franklin County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of December 2007."
